🌿 Take Away

The journey of Sarga 179 is not from ignorance to knowledge.

It is from identification with appearances to abidance in Pure Awareness.

When Consciousness is recognized as one's own Self,

the world is no longer a problem to solve—

it becomes a transparent expression of Brahman.

